March 10, 2025 - Marvel Music was a short-lived Imprint of Marvel Comics that published stories about famous musicians and bands. While some of the stories followed the artist's real life, others featured works of fiction starring the artist. The imprint proved unpopular, only running from 1994 to 1995.
